eb/20111102130156/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-15365179 |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員。首部出演的電影為《{{link-en|放學後 (電影)|Afterschool|放學後}}》（2008年），之後陸續出演了《{{link-en|非典型家庭|Another Happy Day}}》（2011年）、《[[凱文怎麼了？|凱文怎麼了？]]》（2011年），以及《[[壁花男孩|壁花男孩]]》（2012年）。他也在電影《[[怪獸與牠們的產地_(電影)|怪獸與牠們的產地]]》（2016年）及其後續集中飾演魁登斯·巴波（{{lang|en|Credence Barebone}}）。

自2016年的《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》起，米勒於[[DC擴展宇宙|DC擴展宇宙]]中飾演改編自[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]的超級英雄角色[[閃電俠_(貝瑞·艾倫)|貝瑞·艾倫／閃電俠]]。

== 早期生活 ==
米勒於[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]{{link-en|威科夫 (紐澤西州)|Wyckoff, New Jersey|威科夫}}出生和成長<ref>Beckerman, Jim; and Rohan, Virginia. [http://www.northjersey.com/arts_entertainment/138023858_Our_picks_for_Oscar_s_top_honors.html "Our picks for Oscar's top honors"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.northjersey.com/arts_entertainment/138023858_Our_picks_for_Oscar_s_top_honors.html |date=20131224100211 }}, ''[[The_Record_(Bergen_County)|The Record (Bergen County)]]'', 2012-01-25. Accessed 2012-06-07. "And what happened to Tilda Swinton, Leonardo DiCaprio and Wyckoff's Ezra Miller (a Best Supporting Actor possibility for "We Need to Talk About Kevin")?"</ref><ref name=autogenerated3>{{cite web|last=Bosworth|first=Kate|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/ezra-miller/|title=Ezra Miller|work=[[Interview_(magazine)|Interview]]|quote=|date=|accessdate=2011-05-15|archive-date=2011-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510135651/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/ezra-miller|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Lamble |first=David |url=http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=976 |title=The Bay Area Reporter Online | We need to talk about Ezra Miller |publisher=Ebar.com |date= |accessdate=2012-03-23 |archive-date=2012-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305141648/http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=976 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。母親瑪爾塔（{{lang|en|Marta}}），娘家姓柯赫（{{lang|en|Koch}}），是一名現代舞蹈家，而父親勞勃·S·米勒（{{lang|en|Robert S. Miller}}）是{{link-en|海波圖書|Hyperion Books}}的高級副總裁兼總經理主任，後來自行成立{{link-en|沃克曼出版公司|Workman Publishing Company}}<ref name=autogenerated4>{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.co.uk/cgi/news/release?id=50644 |title=Walt Disney Company To Reorganise Publishing Business: Disney Publishing, Worldwide And Hyperion |publisher=Prnewswire.co.uk |date=1999-04-12 |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archive-date=2013-08-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JDmdhT4o?url=http://www.prnewswire.co.uk/news-releases/walt-disney-company-to-reorganise-publishing-business-disney-publishing-worldwide-and-hyperion-156238945.html |dead-url=no }} and is now the President of Macmillan's newest imprint, Flatiron Books.</ref><ref name=nymg1>{{Cite news|last=Yuan|first=Jada|coauthors=|title=We Need to Talk About Ezra|pages=|publisher=New York Magazine|date=2012-01-08|url=http://nymag.com/movies/features/ezra-miller-2012-1/|accessdate=2012-01-11|archive-date=2012-10-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BkPr12iT?url=http://nymag.com/movies/features/ezra-miller-2012-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米勒有兩位姐姐，分別為賽亞（{{lang|en|Saiya}}）與凱特琳（{{lang|en|Caitlin}}）<ref name=nymg1/><ref name=vgou1>{{Cite web |url=http://i43.tinypic.com/vf829l.jpg |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-30 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305005912/http://i43.tinypic.com/vf829l.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref>。父親是猶太人<ref>{{cite web|first=Michael|last=Moran|url=https://www.thejc.com/news/the-diary/meet-the-latest-jewish-superhero-1.448384|title=Meet The Flash, the latest Jewish superhero|work=The Jewish Chronicle|date=2017-11-20|accessdate=2018-05-05|archive-date=2020-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312134459/https://www.thejc.com/news/the-diary/meet-the-latest-jewish-superhero-1.448384|dead-url=no}}</ref>。母親擁有[[德国|德國]]血統和[[荷兰|荷蘭]]血統，是位基督徒<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ezra Miller|url=https://ethnicelebs.com/ezra-miller|access-date=2022-04-20|date=2011-12-21|last=|work=Ethnicity of Celebs {{!}} What Nationality Ancestry Race|language=|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502102722/http://ethnicelebs.com/ezra-miller}}</ref>。米勒認為自己具有[[猶太人|猶太人]]的血統和「精神」<ref name=reps1>{{Cite news|last=Lamble|first=David|coauthors=|title=Family estrangement|pages=|publisher=The Bay Area Reporter|date=2011-12-08|url=http://www.cpanel.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=946|accessdate=2012-01-11|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426042742/http://www.cpanel.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=film&article=946|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=hrt1>{{Cite news|last=Saar|first=Yuval|coauthors=|title=Ezra's Way (Weekend)|pages=|publisher=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]|date=2012-01-19|url=http://www.haaretz.co.il/magazine/1.1620442|accessdate=2012-06-01|quote="My father is Jewish, my mother is not, but I consider myself entirely Jewish even though according to Jewish law I am not. I encourage everyone to understand that the rules were written before anyone could do DNA tests... I know that I am a descendant of Abraham through my father." And a visit to Israel? "I definitely plan to do this."|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224235412/http://www.haaretz.co.il/magazine/1.1620442|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6歲時，米勒開始進行成為歌劇演唱家的訓練，幫助他克服語言上的障礙<ref name = out />。他曾在[[大都會歌劇院|大都會歌劇院]]演唱過，並也在美國首演的[[菲利普·格拉斯|菲利普·格拉斯]]的歌劇《{{lang|en|White Raven}}》中演出<ref name=autogenerated3 />。米勒曾就讀{{link-en|羅克蘭國家走讀學校|Rockland Country Day School}}和{{link-en|哈得遜學院|The Hudson School}}，但在電影《{{link-en|放學後 (電影)|Afterschool|放學後}}》上映後，他就已申請輟學<ref name=nymg1/><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.thecinemasource.com/blog/interviews/ezra-miller-interview-for-beware-the-gonzo/ |title=Ezra Miller Interview for Beware the Gonzo |publisher=The Cinema Source |date=2011-09-08 |accessdate=2011-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928071241/http://www.thecinemasource.com/blog/interviews/ezra-miller-interview-for-beware-the-gonzo/ |archivedate=2011-09-28 }}</ref><ref name=dsblse>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/18/ezra-miller-on-perks-of-being-a-wallflower-being-bisexual-more.html |title=Ezra Miller on ‘Perks of Being a Wallflower,’ Being Bisexual & More - The Daily Beast<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-10-17 |archive-date=2017-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504190928/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/18/ezra-miller-on-perks-of-being-a-wallflower-being-bisexual-more.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

米勒除了演員外還是鼓手，並加入了名為{{lang|en|Sons of an Illustrious Father}}的紐約樂團<ref name=littlewhitelies>{{cite web |author=Little White Lies magazine |url=http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/interviews/ezra-miller-16817 |title=Ezra Miller interview |publisher=littlewhitelies.co.uk |date=2011-10-19 |accessdate=2011-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111025182115/http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/interviews/ezra-miller-16817 |archivedate=2011-10-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sonsofanillustriousfather.com/ |title=SONS |publisher=Sons of an Illustrious Father |date= |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110012737/http://sonsofanillustriousfather.com/ |archive-date=2012-01-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 職業生涯 ==
於2008年與安東尼奧·坎波斯合演的電影《{{link-en|放學後 (電影)|Afterschool|放學後}}》開始了米勒的電影生涯，他在當中飾演寄宿學校中的其中一位少年<ref name=autogenerated3 />。在此之後，米勒與[[安迪·賈西亞|安迪·賈西亞]]、[[茱莉安娜·瑪格里斯|茱莉安娜·瑪格里斯]]、[[史蒂芬·史崔特|史蒂芬·史崔特]]共同出演於2009年的《{{link-en|我的怪咖家庭|City Island (film)}}》。而後又參演了2010年的《{{link-en|每一天 (電影)|Every Day (film)|每一天}}》和《{{link-en|剛左檔案|Beware the Gonzo}}》，這兩部皆首映於[[翠貝卡電影節|翠貝卡電影節]]。米勒接下了和[[約翰·C·萊利|約翰·C·萊利]]、[[蒂妲·絲雲頓|蒂妲·絲雲頓]]合演的[[英國廣播公司電影|BBC電影]]製作的《[[凱文怎麼了？|凱文怎麼了？]]》（2011年），導演為[[琳恩·拉姆賽|琳恩·拉姆賽]]，是一部改編自美國作家[[蘭諾·絲薇佛|蘭諾·絲薇佛]]的2003年同名小說。這部電影在[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]造成了轟動，贏得一致好評<ref>{{cite web|last=Bamigboye|first=Baz|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1386542/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-Im-old-lothario-says-Jude-Law.html|title=BAZ BAMIGBOYE: 'I'm too old to be a lothario', says Jude Law|work=Daily Mail|quote=|date=2011-05-13|accessdate=2011-05-15|archive-date=2011-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514161923/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1386542/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-Im-old-lothario-says-Jude-Law.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Ezra_Miller_at_the_2009_Tribeca_Film_Festival.jpg|180px]]。]]
米勒被[[Showtime_Networks|Showtime Networks]]選中在電視喜劇《[[加州靡情|加州靡情]]》中飾演戴米安<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite web |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/story/ezra-miller-cleared-on-drug-charge_1231177 |title=Ezra Miller | Ezra Miller Cleared On Drug Charge |publisher=Contactmusic |date= |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archive-date=2013-08-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JDmhlbJY?url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/ezra-miller-cleared-on-drug-charge_1231177 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年至2010年，他還現身於《[[慾海醫心|慾海醫心]]》的兩季中。米勒和[[羅根·勒曼|羅根·勒曼]]、[[艾瑪·華森|艾瑪·華森]]一同於改編自[[壁花男孩_(小說)|同名小說]]的電影《[[壁花男孩|壁花男孩]]》中主演。該片於2012年9月21日上映<ref>{{cite web|last=Wilkinson|first=Amy|url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2011/05/19/ezra-miller-perks-of-being-a-wallflower|title=Ezra Miller To Play Patrick In 'Perks of Being a Wallflower'|work=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=2011-05-19|accessdate=2011-05-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520224954/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2011/05/19/ezra-miller-perks-of-being-a-wallflower/|archivedate=2011-05-20}}</ref>。該片獲得普遍好評，使米勒更加出名並入圍諸多獎項。

2014年10月15日，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣布，米勒將於2018年的[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]改編[[超級英雄電影|超級英雄電影]]《閃電俠》中飾演[[閃電俠_(貝瑞·艾倫)|貝瑞·艾倫／閃電俠]]<ref>[http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-flash-movie-ezra-miller-aquaman-jason-momoa-2018-1201330654 "‘The Flash’ Movie to Star Ezra Miller, Out in 2018"] {{Wayback|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-flash-movie-ezra-miller-aquaman-jason-momoa-2018-1201330654 |date=20201120075954 }}. Variety.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-flash-movie-star-741019|title=Warner Bros.' 'The Flash' Movie to Star Ezra Miller|author=|date=2014-10-15|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016001632/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-flash-movie-star-741019|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年時，他率先以閃電俠一角於《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》和《[[自殺突擊隊|自殺突擊隊]]》中出現。同於2016年，米勒於《[[怪獸與牠們的產地_(電影)|怪獸與牠們的產地]]》中飾演魁登斯·巴波（{{lang|en|Credence Barebone}}）一角，該片為《[[哈利波特系列電影|哈利波特]]》系列電影的衍生及前傳電影，在上映後獲得了成功的口碑，並在之後回歸續集演出。他在2017年的《[[正義聯盟_(電影)|正義聯盟]]》中出演閃電俠，更於2020年在電視劇《[[綠箭俠_(電視劇)|綠箭俠]]》的跨界聯動集「[[無限地球危機_(綠箭宇宙)|無限地球危機]]」中客串該角。

2020年，米勒加入[[派拉蒙+|派拉蒙+]]電視迷你劇《[[末日逼近_(2020年迷你劇)|末日逼近]]》，飾演垃圾桶人（{{lang|en|Trashcan Man}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/fashion/article/ezra-miller-interview|title=Ezra Miller: 'We're not fighting for equality. We are fighting for regard of our supremacy'|website=GQ|last=GQ Style magazine|date=2020-03-12|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119025516/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/fashion/article/ezra-miller-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/ezra-miller-the-stand/|title=Ezra Miller reveals his wild top-secret role in The Stand|website=EW|last=Hibberd|first=James|date=2020-11-18|access-date=2020-11-18|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119025510/https://ew.com/tv/ezra-miller-the-stand/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該劇於2020年12月首播<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2020/08/25/the-stand-premiere-date-stephen-king-cbs-all-access/|title=The Stand Miniseries Lands December Premiere Date on CBS All Access|website=TVLine|first=Dave|last=Nemetz|date=2020-08-25|access-date=2020-08-25|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825160143/https://tvline.com/2020/08/25/the-stand-premiere-date-stephen-king-cbs-all-access/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
=== 性取向和關係 ===
米勒曾形容自己是[[酷兒|酷兒]]：「這讓我試著踏出原本的生活圈，用不一樣的眼光看待這個世界，所以我想這也是為什麼許多偉大的思想是來自那些被排斥和剝奪權利的人。」在2012年宣傳《[[壁花男孩|壁花男孩]]》時，他便在訪問中出櫃示自己是[[同性戀|同性戀]]者，但之後卻收到不少警告，有人告訴他，好萊塢許多同性戀或雙性戀會選擇隱藏性向，是因為出櫃會失去許多片約，甚至喪失成為影帝的機會，但他不以為意<ref name = out>{{cite web|author=Shana Naomi Krochmal|url=http://www.out.com/entertainment/movies/2012/08/15/perks-wallflower-ezra-miller-logan-lerman-johnny-simmons?page=0,2|title=Lost & Found|publisher=[[Out_Magazine|Out Magazine]]|date=2012-08-15|accessdate=2012-08-15|archive-date=2012-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819000932/http://www.out.com/entertainment/movies/2012/08/15/perks-wallflower-ezra-miller-logan-lerman-johnny-simmons?page=0,2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他使用[[单数they|它們這個代詞]]，《[[GQ|GQ]]》表示，這樣做是「針對拒絕性別歧視」<ref name="lgbtqnation">{{cite news |last1=Bollinger |first1=Alex |title=Actor Ezra Miller says they don't identify as a man or a woman |url=https://www.lgbtqnation.com/2018/11/actor-ezra-miller-says-doesnt-identify-man-woman/ |work=LGBTQ Nation |date=2018-11-08 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428084144/https://www.lgbtqnation.com/2018/11/actor-ezra-miller-says-doesnt-identify-man-woman/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

米勒透露曾與某好萊塢製片人和導演有過[[＃MeToo|＃MeToo]]的經歷，但均未透露姓名。米勒說：「他們給了我酒，但我未成年。他們就像『嘿，想參加我們關於同性戀革命的電影嗎？』我當時想，『不，你們是怪物。』」米勒接著表示支持#MeToo運動。<ref name="lgbtqnation" />

2010年，米勒在拍攝《{{link-en|剛左檔案|Beware the Gonzo}}》期間，與[[柔伊·克拉維茲|柔伊·克拉維茲]]交往過<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://liverampup.com/entertainment/ezra-miller-gay-girlfriend-boyfriend-dating-ethnicity.html|title=Ezra Miller aka Flash Says 'I'm Queer' Not Gay; Boyfriend & Dating Amid Confusion?|date=2019-05-16|work=Liverampup.com|access-date=2019-09-08|archive-date=2019-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222130219/http://liverampup.com/entertainment/ezra-miller-gay-girlfriend-boyfriend-dating-ethnicity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，米勒透露自己與多人（包含{{lang|en|Sons of an Illustrious Father}}）的成員處於[[多邊戀|多邊戀]]的關係<ref>{{Cite web|last=Gajewski|first=Ryan|date=2018-11-15|title=The Magic of Ezra Miller|url=https://www.playboy.com/read/ezra-miller-fantastic-beasts-interview|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420002054/https://www.playboy.com/read/ezra-miller-fantastic-beasts-interview|archive-date=2021-04-20|access-date=2021-02-12|work=[[Playboy|Playboy]]}}</ref>。

